[
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我现在才发觉我根本就不应该带你来的。",
    "tone": "后悔",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "text": "为什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我真怕你看见她的时候会失态。",
    "tone": "担忧",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "在她那种人的面前，你只要说错了一句话，就害死人了。",
    "tone": "警告",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "text": "你用不着担心，什么样的人我没见过？",
    "tone": "自信",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我也知道你见过不少人，各式各样的人你都见过，只可惜你现在要去见的根本不是一个人。",
    "tone": "感慨",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "text": "不是人，是什么？",
    "tone": "好奇",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "是九天仙子被谪落凡尘。",
    "tone": "神秘",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
    "text": "老婆婆，我姓金，我以前来过，我想你一定还记得我，上次也是你替我开门的。",
    "tone": "恭敬",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
    "text": "这是我的朋友，他叫陆小凤，我是带他来见你们宫主的。",
    "tone": "客气",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
    "text": "麻烦你去告诉你们的宫主，一定要请他好好的吃一顿，好好的喝几杯酒。",
    "tone": "托付",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "陆小鸟，你多多保重，万事留心，我们后会有期。",
    "tone": "告别",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "text": "你的意思是不是说，你现在就要走了？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "是的。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "text": "你现在怎么可以走？",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我现在为什么不可以走？",
    "tone": "理直气壮",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你要见宫素素，现在我已经把你带来了，而且已经叫她请你吃饭、喝酒。",
    "tone": "解释",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
    "speaker_name": "金七两",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我已经把答应过你的事全都做到了，此时不走，更待何时？",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "喂，你这个人，你是来干什么的？",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "我是专程来拜见宫主的，我有个朋友说宫主一定会见我。",
    "tone": "客气",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你那个朋友是什么东西？你又是什么东西？凭什么闯到这里来？",
    "tone": "敌意",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "我不是东西，我是个人。",
    "tone": "幽默",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "这句话我已经不知道跟别人说过多少次了，别人为什么总是看不出这一点？",
    "tone": "自嘲",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "幸好我早就看出来了。",
    "tone": "讽刺",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "看出了什么？",
    "tone": "追问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "看出你根本就不是个东西，所以你最好还是赶快走远一点，免得我生气。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "我本来是要走的，如果你是宫主，我早就走了。",
    "tone": "讽刺",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "幸好我也早就看出来了。",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你又看出了什么？",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "看出你不是宫主。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "你全身上下连一点宫主的样子都没有。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "其实我并不怪你，你虽然一直在跟我大吼大叫，乱发脾气，我也可以原谅你。",
    "tone": "谅解",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "因为我知道一个女人到了你这样的年纪还嫁不出去，火气总是难免特别大的。",
    "tone": "讽刺",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你想干什么？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "我什么都不想干。",
    "tone": "无辜",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你为什么要抓住我的脚？",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "因为你要踢我。",
    "tone": "解释",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你放开。",
    "tone": "命令",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "我不能放开。",
    "tone": "拒绝",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "为什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "因为我不想被你一脚踢死。",
    "tone": "幽默",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
    "speaker_name": "老太婆",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你不能放开她的脚，难道你想就这么样把她的脚握在手里，握一辈子？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "宫萍，你不要再跟陆公子胡闹了，还是快请他进来吧！",
    "tone": "命令",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
    "speaker_name": "老太婆",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "小伙子，如果我是你，我是绝不会松手的，我保证只要你的手一松开，你的肚子马上就会被人踢一脚。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
    "speaker_name": "老太婆",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "陆小凤，你果然不是东西，现在连我这个已经老得快瞎了眼的老太婆都看出来了。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "陆公子，我们素昧平生，从无来往，你一定要见我，是不是有什么特别的事？",
    "tone": "礼貌",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "没有。",
    "tone": "否认",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "连一点特别的事都没有。",
    "tone": "强调",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "那么你是为了什么一定要见我？",
    "tone": "追问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我明白你的感觉，现在你心里一定觉得很失望，因为你一定想不到我已经这么老了。",
    "tone": "理解",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "年纪大了的女人，就和走了味的酒一样，陆公子都不会有兴趣的。",
    "tone": "自嘲",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "只不过陆公子的大名，我也是久仰的，你既然来了，我也想留你喝杯酒。",
    "tone": "客气",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "可是我也知道，这顿酒你一定会喝得很难受。",
    "tone": "坦诚",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "我很想说几句话，却不知道是不是应该说出来。",
    "tone": "犹豫",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你说。",
    "tone": "鼓励",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "不管你的年纪有多大，你都是我这一生中所见到的最温柔最可爱的女人。",
    "tone": "真诚",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "这是实话，不知道你信不信。",
    "tone": "诚恳",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我当然相信。",
    "tone": "感动",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "就算你说这些话只不过为了要安慰我，我也宁可相信它是真的。",
    "tone": "感动",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "我也希望宫主刚才说的是真话，是真的想留下我来喝杯酒。",
    "tone": "期待",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "如果是真的呢？",
    "tone": "反问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "那么我就希望宫主说的不是一杯酒了。",
    "tone": "期待",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "能够和宫主这样的美人喝酒，我最少也要喝上个三五百杯。",
    "tone": "豪爽",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "难怪别人都说陆小凤是个可爱的男人，连我这个老太婆看见都喜欢，何况那些小姑娘。",
    "tone": "赞叹",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "陆公子，我一直听说你是个最懂得怜香惜玉的人，可是现在看你的样子却实在不值得恭维。",
    "tone": "批评",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你实在令人失望。",
    "tone": "失望",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "老实说，连我自己都对我自己觉得有点失望。",
    "tone": "自嘲",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "依我看来，一个挑粪的，对女孩子的态度都要比你好一点。",
    "tone": "讽刺",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "依我看来，大概还不止好一点，至少也要好七、八、九十点。",
    "tone": "自嘲",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "那你为什么这样做呢？",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你是不是喝醉了？",
    "tone": "怀疑",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "我没有醉。",
    "tone": "否认",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "我可以保证，我比世上任何一个挑粪的都要清醒七、八、九十倍。",
    "tone": "自嘲",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你这样做，究竟想干什么？",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
    "text": "其实我也不想干什么，只不过想请她的裤子暂时离开一下，好让我看看她的腿。",
    "tone": "无赖",
    "chapter": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
    "speaker_name": "宫素素",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
